title: Myanmar  CPI Housing Utilities
description: CPI Housing Utilities in Myanmar increased to 236.55 points in June from 232.50 points in May of 2022. CPI Housing Utilities in Myanmar averaged 153.51 points from 2013 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 236.55 points in June of 2022 and a record low of 103.93 points in January of 2013. This page provides - Myanmar  Cpi Housing Utilities- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistics Organization, Myanmar
